{"tid":2159310,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴塞當年唔簽戴維斯因為","createTime":"2020-08-16T08:57:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T19:44:09.000Z","uid":72497,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"118794b74e847409438c98b4bf160494c862db23","tid":2159310,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:57:26.000Z","msg":"原來巴塞隆拿當年有機會簽入左閘阿方素戴維斯，但竟然以他是加拿大人為理由拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n19歲的阿方素戴維斯（Alphonso Davies）今季以極速上位，於拜仁慕尼黑以8:2血洗巴塞隆拿的歐聯8強，在左路把巴塞右閘施美度玩弄於股掌之中。 西班牙著名體育記者Luis Omar Tapia於Twitter爆料，指巴塞曾經有機會搶先拜仁，從溫哥華白帽簽入阿方素戴維斯：「在阿方素戴維斯加盟拜仁前數個月，史岱哲哥夫曾經向巴度姆推薦這位小將，不過巴度姆的反應是『他是加拿大人，不了』。」 <br />\n<br />\n巴塞可說是走寶，事關阿方素戴維斯的表現有目共睹，就連皇家馬德里左閘馬些路也忍不住在Instagram盛讚：「當我看你踢球，你為我的眼睛帶來歡愉。」"},{"pid":"c53370f92c2588e680dcc55e60f3f263b1a87505","tid":2159310,"uid":40267,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:58:39.000Z","msg":"我以為得美國人先會笑加拿大人"},{"pid":"446faaac9c3b6b31430974039f8a0fc48bc2cc28","tid":2159310,"uid":71433,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:00:03.000Z","msg":"細佬又抽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb26ad3c829fa04e75e046f4de517ac7d4f65a20","tid":2159310,"uid":266467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:02:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f157228d8eda4322a65846ef8933c0e50d1d927","tid":2159310,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"446faaac9c3b6b31430974039f8a0fc48bc2cc28","tid":2159310,"uid":71433,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:00:03.000Z","msg":"細佬又抽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:02:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51edd046eab24ffb972448efc9174f95b71abb5b","t